# Normalize line endings across machines.
#
# Everything is stored and checked out as LF — including on Windows — so
# moving this repo between macOS and a Windows PC never rewrites files,
# never triggers phantom "whole file changed" diffs, and Vite/Node stay
# happy. Git handles this transparently; you don't have to configure
# anything on the Windows side.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — Git must never touch these
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif  binary
*.ico  binary
*.webp binary
*.woff  binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf   binary
*.eot   binary
*.mp3   binary
*.mp4   binary
